thread.title: Hillary Clinton Merchandise Now 75 Percent Off at DC Store
thread.title_full: Hillary Clinton Merchandise Now 75 Percent Off at DC Store

author: Chandler Gill
title: Hillary Clinton Merchandise Now 75 Percent Off at DC Store
text:
Failed Democratic presidential nominee Hillary Clinton now has merchandise with her face and name on it being sold at a 75 percent discount in a Washington, D.C. store. Fox Business host Maria Bartiromo tweeted a photo this week that showed coffee and travel mugs with Clinton’s face and name being sold at a major discount, Fox News reported Wednesday.
Some of the mugs also had the year 2016 written under Clinton’s name.
Stumbled upon this in DC @MorningsMaria @FoxBusiness pic.twitter.com/SZAqjHcEZk 
— Maria Bartiromo (@MariaBartiromo) January 17, 2017 
The average cost of Clinton mugs on the internet is around $15.00.
However, Clinton fans are out of luck if they wish to purchase merchandise from hillaryclinton.com, because now the “shop” link redirects to the official store for the Democratic Party.
What a deal for Clinton supporters, though.
